title: Nvidia Is Investing in Biotech Like Wild. Here's What It Means for the Stock.
text: Nvidia is forging collaborations and making investments in biotech. It's positioning to facilitate using artificial intelligence for drug discovery.

title: 5 Nasdaq Composite Laggards Likely to Gather Pace in 2024

title: Bitcoin to Shine in 2024: Are These 5 Stocks on Your Radar?
text: Stocks like NVIDIA Corporation (NVDA), Coinbase Global (COIN), Block (SQ), Interactive Brokers Group (IBKR) and PayPal Holdings (PYPL) are likely to benefit in the near term form the Bitcoin rally.
